		"html_code" : "<!-- ============================================================= -->\n<!-- IBSRELA header banner — plug-and-play section                 -->\n<!-- Drop this <mj-wrapper> into the <mj-body> of a larger MJML.    -->\n<!-- Navy panel: #262262                                            -->\n<!-- ============================================================= -->\n\n<mj-wrapper border=\"1px solid #000000\" padding=\"0\" background-color=\"#ffffff\">\n\n  <!-- View in Browser bar -->\n  <mj-section background-color=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"8px 14px\">\n    <mj-column padding=\"0\">\n      <mj-text align=\"right\" font-family=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" font-size=\"13px\" line-height=\"18px\" color=\"#262626\" padding=\"0\">\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"color:#262626; text-decoration:underline;\">View in Browser<\/a>\n      <\/mj-text>\n    <\/mj-column>\n  <\/mj-section>\n\n  <!-- Logo + message -->\n  <mj-section background-color=\"#262262\" padding=\"0\">\n\n    <!-- Left: logo on white -->\n    <mj-column width=\"32%\" background-color=\"#ffffff\" vertical-align=\"middle\" padding=\"0\">\n      <mj-image\n        src=\"https:\/\/solstice-public-forever.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com\/design_library\/affda42b-9fe3-4320-8f85-de496892905d\/7772aba5-1ff5-4985-80bf-c15b782111a4\/bulk\/20260602_162451_060218_IBSRELA_50mg_DPT_CMYK_v02.png\"\n        alt=\"IBSRELA (tenapanor) tablets 50 mg\"\n        width=\"150px\"\n        align=\"center\"\n        padding=\"18px 10px\" \/>\n    <\/mj-column>\n\n    <!-- Right: message on navy -->\n    <mj-column width=\"68%\" background-color=\"#262262\" vertical-align=\"middle\" padding=\"0\">\n      <mj-text align=\"left\" font-family=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17px\" line-height=\"24px\" color=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"18px 20px\">\n        Please see the <a href=\"#\" style=\"color:#ffffff; text-decoration:underline;\">Medication Guide<\/a> and full <a href=\"#\" style=\"color:#ffffff; text-decoration:underline;\">Prescribing Information<\/a>, including Boxed Warning, related to risk of severe dehydration in children.\n      <\/mj-text>\n    <\/mj-column>\n\n  <\/mj-section>\n\n<\/mj-wrapper>",
